claim.claim-text:
1. A phase change memory device comprising a phase change material, wherein the phase change material is a compound of:
(i) Ga;
(ii) La or La and at least one further lanthanide element; and
(iii) chalcogenide;
wherein the lanthanide is composed of La and the chalcogenide is composed of S;
wherein the ratio of Ga:S atoms is approximately 2:3, and the ratio of La:S atoms is approximately 2:3; and
wherein the ratio of Ga to La is 3:1, so that the ratio of atoms of Ga:La:S is approximately 3:1:6.
